<promed@promedmail.org>
[This is the 1st confirmation of avian influenza A (H5N1) virus infection
in the family group in which person-to-person transmission of infection was
suspected. Unfortunately, the body of the young girl, who was the index
case, has been cremated. It is unclear from this report whether her
deceased mother has been confirmed as a case of avian influenza virus
infection. - Mod.CP]
[Updates on the avian influenza situation in Thailand, including numbers of
suspected cases reported and cases currently under investigation can be
found on the Thai Ministry of Health website
<http://thaigcd.ddc.moph.go.th/Bird_Flu_main_en.html>. - Mod. MPP]
